  "error": null
}
```

## Error Output
```json
{
  "command": "assign",
  "subcommand": "clear",
  "session": "myproject",
  "timestamp": "2026-01-19T12:00:00Z",
  "success": false,
  "data": null,
  "warnings": [],
  "error": {
    "code": "NOT_ASSIGNED",
    "message": "bead bd-xyz is not currently assigned"
